    narr:generatedFrom "8d8c27340c2636713f8a3aa793053637113596bc" ;
    narr:narration """This hub is the verbatim record of the aswritten narrative — direct speech and attributed observations spanning January 2026 through July 2026, with one earlier witness from July 2025. The corpus opens with the March 2026 product-demonstrating-itself cluster: [Scarlet's modular-synthesizer feeling](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_ScarletModularSynthesizerQuote) and [\"This is incredible\"](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_ScarletIncredibleQuote) capture the emergent quality of the interview-driven strategy session. April 2026 surfaces the buyer-side thesis in the customer's CTO's own voice: [perspective and collaboration over information and code](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_CustomerCTOInformationCommodity) and [the AI slop diagnosis](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_CustomerCTOAISlopQuote) — the economic buyer independently naming the exact problem. May 2026 builds the curated-memory cluster: [the PR-with-unit-tests metaphor](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_CustomerCTOPRMetaphorQuote), [Scarlet's human-review framing](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_ScarletCantAutomateQuote), [the customer's chief architect's discomfort with unreviewed dumps](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_CustomerArchitectNotComfortableQuote), and [Scarlet's base-camp self-assessment](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_BaseCampQuote) marking the moment. Also in May, a citation-architecture thread emerges: [the constellation frame](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_ScarletQuote_Constellation), [the reductionist-frame diagnosis](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_ScarletQuote_Reductionist), and [the primary-uniqueness refinement](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_ScarletQuote_PrimaryUnique). April 2026 also holds an SMS/channel debate — [spam pushback from outside-tech beta users](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_OutsideTechBetaUserSpamPushback), [Scarlet's enterprise-only leaning](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_ScarletSMSEnterpriseLeaning), and [fraud-cost accounting](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_ScarletSMSFraudCost) — unresolved as of that date. July 2026 closes with [Scarlet's verdict on June 10](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_ScarletVerdictQuote), [the deli-email opinionated-perspective signal](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_DeliEmailOpinionatedQuote), and [Tony's pain-first words](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_TonyPainFirstQuote). The governing style is [direct block-quoted speech as primary evidence](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_DirectQuoteStyle), with analysis kept separate from the quoted material.""" ;
